CHAPTER 28 ‚Äì SharePoint REST API (Full Reference)

REST Endpoint:

https://tenant.sharepoint.com/_api/

Common Operations

‚úî Get List Items

/_api/web/lists/getbytitle('ListName')/items

‚úî Create Item

POST /_api/web/lists/getbytitle('ListName')/items

‚úî Get Libraries

/_api/web/lists?$filter=BaseTemplate eq 101

‚úî Upload File

/_api/web/GetFolderByServerRelativeUrl('/Library')/Files/add(...)

‚úî User Info

/_api/web/currentuser


---

CHAPTER 29 ‚Äì Microsoft Graph API (Advanced)

Graph API is the universal API for Microsoft 365.

Common Scenarios

Fetch Teams info

List OneDrive files

Get user profile photos

Access Planner tasks

Read Outlook mails

Search across Microsoft 365


Graph Endpoint:

https://graph.microsoft.com/v1.0/


---

CHAPTER 30 ‚Äì PnP JS Library (Simple & Fast)

PnPJS helps call SharePoint APIs easily.

Examples

‚úî Get items:

const items = await sp.web.lists.getByTitle("List").items();

‚úî Add item:

sp.web.lists.getByTitle("List").items.add({ Title: "New Item" });

‚úî Get files:

sp.web.getFolderByServerRelativeUrl("/Library").files();


---

CHAPTER 31 ‚Äì PnP PowerShell (Admin Automation)

Common Commands

‚úî Connect to SharePoint:

Connect-PnPOnline -Url https://tenant.sharepoint.com

‚úî List all sites:

Get-PnPTenantSite

‚úî Create site:

New-PnPSite -Type TeamSite -Title "NewSite"

‚úî Export site permissions:

Get-PnPSitePermission

‚úî Add content type:

Add-PnPContentType


