CHAPTER 34 ‚Äì Integration with Microsoft Teams

SharePoint powers Teams in the background.

Where SharePoint is used in Teams?

Teams Feature	Backed by SharePoint

Files tab	SharePoint library
Wiki (deprecated)	SharePoint pages
Lists app	SharePoint lists
Document collaboration	SharePoint Online
Teams site	Microsoft 365 Group site


You can add:

SPFx web parts into Teams tabs

SharePoint pages into Teams

Lists/Libraries into Teams



---

CHAPTER 35 ‚Äì OneDrive Deep Architecture

OneDrive = personal SharePoint site.

Features:

Sync engine

Personal vault

Known Folder Move (KFM)

Files on-demand

Auto-save from Office

Ransomware detection


Where OneDrive stores content:

https://tenant-my.sharepoint.com/personal/user/


---

CHAPTER 36 ‚Äì Backup & Recovery in SharePoint Online

SharePoint Online automatically maintains:

‚úî Recycle Bin

93 days retention

Stage 1 + Stage 2 recycle bin


‚úî Version History

Unlimited (if enabled)

Restore older versions individually


‚úî Files Restore

Restore entire library to previous time

Useful after ransomware attack


‚úî No manual backup required

Microsoft manages:

Datacenter redundancy

Geo-redundant storage

Server failover systems


Admins can use:

3rd party backups (AvePoint / Veeam / Datto)



---

CHAPTER 37 ‚Äì Performance Optimization

Tips

Use metadata, avoid deep folder nesting

Use HUB navigation instead of custom menus

Avoid very large lists (>5,000 items in a view)

Use indexed columns

Turn on CDN for modern pages

Minimize custom scripts



