üß© CHAPTER 44 ‚Äì SharePoint Development Models

SharePoint development can be done using:


---

1. REST API (Modern)

Used in:

SPFx

PowerApps

Power Automate

External apps



---

2. Microsoft Graph API

Used for:

User data

Groups

Teams

Files

Permissions



---

3. PnPjs (JavaScript SDK)

Used in:

SPFx web parts

React apps



---

4. PnP PowerShell

Most powerful admin automation.


---

5. CSOM (Client-Side Object Model)

Used in:

C#

PowerShell

Remote apps



---

6. JSOM (JavaScript Object Model)

Legacy model used in classic pages.


---

7. Webhooks

Get notifications when list item changes.


---

8. Search REST API

Used for:

Custom search

Query suggestions

Filtering



