7.7 SharePoint REST API

Base URL:

https://<tenant>.sharepoint.com/_api/

Common REST Endpoints

Purpose	URL

Get lists	/web/lists
Get items	/web/lists/getByTitle('List')/items
Create item	POST ‚Üí /items
Update item	MERGE ‚Üí /items(id)

7.8 Microsoft Graph API (for SharePoint)

Graph is the universal API for Microsoft 365.

Common endpoints:

Purpose	Graph Endpoint

Get site	/sites/{site-id}
Get drive	/drives/{drive-id}
Upload file	/drive/root:/path/file
List DriveItems	/drive/root/children

7.9 PnP JS Library

A wrapper for REST API to reduce code.

Example:

import { sp } from "@pnp/sp";

sp.web.lists.getByTitle("Tasks").items.get();

