8.17 Backup & Restore in SharePoint Online

SharePoint Online automatically manages backup.

Microsoft handles:

14-day point-in-time restore for OneDrive

93-day recycle bin (Site)

93 + 93 days = 186 days (Two-stage recycle bin)

Geo-redundant replication

Item-level restore


Admins control:

Restore files

Restore lists/libraries

Restore site using ‚ÄúSite Restore‚Äù (last 30 days)

