Q39. How do you restore a deleted site?

Admin Center ‚Üí Active sites ‚Üí Deleted sites ‚Üí Restore

Up to 30 days


Q40. What is the difference between sensitivity labels and retention labels?

Feature	Sensitivity	Retention

Purpose	Security / protection	Compliance / retention
Action	Encryption, restrict sharing	Keep / delete after X time
Applies To	SharePoint, OneDrive, Teams	SharePoint, OneDrive, Exchange

10.6 PowerApps + SharePoint + Flow Questions

