Integrate ‚Üí PowerApps ‚Üí Customize form ‚Üí Save & publish


Q42. How to automate approval process for SharePoint?

Power Automate ‚Üí Trigger: When item created ‚Üí Action: Start and wait for approval ‚Üí Update item


Q43. How do you handle delegation warnings?

Use delegable functions

Index SharePoint columns

Avoid unsupported functions like Filter() on large lists


Q44. How to handle attachments in PowerApps?

Use Attachment control

Add / Remove / Download supported

Limit max attachments if required


Q45. How to send daily reports from SharePoint?

Create Flow ‚Üí Trigger: Recurrence

Action: Get items ‚Üí Compose email ‚Üí Send to users

