3. Large storage ‚Üí Increase quota, archive old content, enforce retention.


4. Sensitive files leaked ‚Üí Audit logs, apply DLP, revoke sharing links.


5. Role-based access in PowerApps ‚Üí Load user roles, conditional visibility.


6. Dashboard ‚Üí Gallery + Charts + KPIs + Collections + Filters.


7. Document approval ‚Üí PowerApps form ‚Üí Flow approval ‚Üí Status update ‚Üí Email notifications.

Part H ‚Äì Advanced Troubleshooting
Flow failures ‚Üí Check run history, correct triggers/actions
Delegation warnings ‚Üí Use delegable functions, index columns
Sync errors ‚Üí Reset OneDrive, check naming restrictions
Large data ‚Üí Use indexed columns, filter early, collections in PowerApps

Part I ‚Äì Bonus Interview Tricks
1. Difference questions ‚Üí e.g., Modern vs Classic, Hub vs Team site, Sensitivity vs Retention.
2. Scenario-based ‚Üí e.g., Build leave management, ticketing, adverse events app.
3. Best practices ‚Üí Governance, security, automation, SPFx development.
4. PowerApps performance ‚Üí Collections, delegation, Concurrent(), reduce nested galleries.


