Routing documents to proper library or folder.

3. Chatbots & Virtual Agents
Power Virtual Agents integrated with SharePoint lists.
Answer FAQs and perform automated tasks.

4. Approval Workflows
Multi-level approvals using Power Automate.
Conditional branching for different business scenarios.

